item.title: Delta [random interface]
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

I believe the interface is 2808, so search your server for it. There should be some form of timer that spawns it every now and then. Remove it.

Also, this may be of help: http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/tutorials/108543-delta-getting-rid-little-random-genie.html
